Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…到底是去哪儿啊…我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？哎呀…但是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山我都去过一回了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不是山是树海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去富士的树海好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来是树海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我去啊…
